00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:43,040
You've got a real knack

277
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:46,800
for getting these people
to tell lies for you.

278
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:48,870
Very good. Mr. Shen,

279
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:52,440
after so many years
living with your wife,

280
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:55,160
you wouldn't tell lies, would you?

281
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:59,110
Is this the Mrs. Shen

282
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:01,830
you've always had in mind?

283
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:05,320
Wanning,

284
00:12:05,870 --> 00:12:06,750
stop messing around.

285
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:07,750
Is she

286
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:09,710
your wife?

287
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:19,260
[Prosperous Era]

288
00:12:57,380 --> 00:12:58,040
No.

289
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:02,350
Shen Yurong, what did you say?

290
00:13:02,980 --> 00:13:04,560
How could she not be Xue Fangfei?

291
00:13:04,860 --> 00:13:05,420
You're lying.

292
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:06,560
She's obviously Xue Fangfei!

293
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:07,340
Your Highness,

294
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:10,060
my wife is dead.

295
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:12,130
Even if there was someone

296
00:13:12,130 --> 00:13:13,700
who looked exactly like her,

297
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:15,460
it wouldn't be her.

298
00:13:15,850 --> 00:13:17,100
[Prosperous Era]
Shen Yurong, are you blind?

299
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:18,890
You can't even recognise your own wife?

300
00:13:19,010 --> 00:13:20,770
Your Highness, please mind your words.

301
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:23,700
Don't be disrespectful
in front of His Majesty.

302
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:26,980
It's impossible
that I don't recognise my own wife.

303
00:13:33,220 --> 00:13:34,100
Then let's open the coffin

304
00:13:34,530 --> 00:13:35,180
and examine the bones.

305
00:13:42,010 --> 00:13:43,340
My late wife died in the mountains

306
00:13:44,100 --> 00:13:45,420
and I couldn't find her bones,

307
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:48,250
so I had to build an empty tomb for her.

308
00:13:48,820 --> 00:13:50,220
Your Highness,

309
00:13:51,770 --> 00:13:52,580
what can you examine?

310
00:13:52,770 --> 00:13:54,770
Who says I want
to examine Xue Fangfei's bones?

311
00:13:55,130 --> 00:13:56,460
Xue Fangfei is standing right here

312
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:58,340
and the real Jiang Li
was killed by her long ago.

313
00:13:58,340 --> 00:13:59,420
Her body was buried
on Qingcheng Mountain.

314
00:14:10,010 --> 00:14:10,850
Have you forgotten

315
00:14:10,940 --> 00:14:12,340
that Li didn't go to school

316
00:14:12,370 --> 00:14:13,820
as she's been living in Zhennyu Hall
since she was little?

317
00:14:14,010 --> 00:14:15,820
[Men end up in hills and graveyards.]
The strokes are strong,

318
00:14:16,010 --> 00:14:18,850
straight and neat.

319
00:14:19,250 --> 00:14:21,370
Since ancient times,
people's defense of a criminal

320
00:14:21,490 --> 00:14:24,370
is like the people's offense
against the government.

321
00:14:24,610 --> 00:14:26,300
She doesn't know what she's doing!

322
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:28,820
There are so many
miserable people in the world.

323
00:14:29,130 --> 00:14:31,580
Why did Second Lady Jiang

324
00:14:32,010 --> 00:14:34,650
try to save Xue Huaiyuan at all costs?

325
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:36,700
Grand Chancellor Jiang,

326
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:40,010
Your real daughter, Jiang Li,

327
00:14:40,490 --> 00:14:42,060
was buried on Qingcheng Mountain.

328
00:14:42,820 --> 00:14:44,490
I've found her tomb.

329
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:48,460
If you open the coffin
and let the coroner examine the bones,

330
00:14:48,940 --> 00:14:51,890
you'll know who your real daughter is.

331
00:14:57,580 --> 00:14:58,220
Father,

332
00:14:58,730 --> 00:15:00,100
seems like Her Highness

333
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:02,130
won't let me go today.

334
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:03,820
Guards,

335
00:15:04,490 --> 00:15:05,770
go to Qingcheng Mountain

336
00:15:06,180 --> 00:15:07,370
and bring back the bones immediately.

337
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:12,060
Since Her Highness has made it so clear,

338
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:15,220
I need to give my father an explanation.

339
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:16,820
Because we're father and daughter,

340
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,370
I have caused

341
00:15:19,700 --> 00:15:20,980
you trouble,

342
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:22,770
and the Jiang family is in turmoil,

343
00:15:23,820 --> 00:15:25,490
I'm sorry.

344
00:15:26,010 --> 00:15:27,980
Don't make it sound so grandiose.

345
00:15:28,610 --> 00:15:31,220
I'm trying to rectify
the Jiang family's bloodline.

346
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,460
Your Highness, thank you

347
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,420
for thinking

348
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:36,530
of the Jiang family at this point.

349
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:37,770
If that's the case,

350
00:15:38,650 --> 00:15:39,770
summon the coroner.

351
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:42,060
No need.

352
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:45,700
Your Highness, I've never
had much interaction with you.

353
00:15:46,130 --> 00:15:50,370
I'm flattered that you show such concern

354
00:15:50,370 --> 00:15:52,610
for my family.

355
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:57,460
I'm just not old enough to be confused.

356
00:15:57,890 --> 00:16:01,010
Of course I can recognise
my own daughter.

357
00:16:03,180 --> 00:16:05,820
Don't you want to know

358
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:07,850
who your own daughter is?

359
00:16:08,610 --> 00:16:10,100
It's an offense
of deceiving His Majesty.

360
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,650
Your Highness,

361
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:15,370
I know my daughter's offended
a lot of people

362
00:16:15,610 --> 00:16:17,060
trying to overturn
a good official's case.

363
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:21,130
But my daughter tried her best

364
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:22,610
to overcome all the difficulties,

365
00:16:22,850 --> 00:16:26,300
so I can't be left behind.

366
00:16:26,580 --> 00:16:29,820
If I can't even recognise my own family,

367
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:32,610
I'll be ashamed

368
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:36,940
to face the ancestors
of the Jiang family in the afterlife.

369
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:42,010
Your Majesty's time should not be spent
on the family affairs of the Jiangs.

370
00:16:42,730 --> 00:16:45,340
Now that the Xue Huaiyuan
corruption case is over,

371
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:49,220
I'll take my daughter home.

372
00:16:53,140 --> 00:16:54,300
[Prosperous Era]

373
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,130
Grand Chancellor Jiang,

374
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:56,850
I must examine

375
00:16:57,420 --> 00:16:58,530
the bones today.

376
00:16:58,850 --> 00:16:59,610
Enough!

377
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:00,730
Your Majesty,

378
00:17:01,370 --> 00:17:02,530
you're the emperor.

379
00:17:03,010 --> 00:17:05,220
How can you allow
these people to deceive you?

380
00:17:05,220 --> 00:17:06,380
How can you uphold your authority?

381
00:17:06,380 --> 00:17:07,090
Wanning,

382
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:09,050
I've already put up with you a lot.

383
00:17:09,810 --> 00:17:11,010
If you keep this up,

384
00:17:11,770 --> 00:17:13,460
you'll be acting treacherously.

385
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:16,700
[Prosperous Era]

386
00:17:16,730 --> 00:17:18,490
Today's good mood
of vindicating a good official

387
00:17:18,490 --> 00:17:19,660
has been ruined by you.

388
00:17:19,980 --> 00:17:21,290
You have no regard
for the rules of the palace,

389
00:17:21,460 --> 00:17:22,900
and you behave recklessly
in Imperial Court today.

390
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:23,900
You're so wrong!

391
00:17:24,570 --> 00:17:25,220
Guards!

392
00:17:25,460 --> 00:17:27,140
Take Eldest Princess back
to her residence!

393
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:29,900
Let go.

394
00:17:30,570 --> 00:17:31,250
Let go of me.

395
00:17:31,770 --> 00:17:32,290
Let go.

396
00:17:32,570 --> 00:17:33,490
Let go!

397
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:36,980
I'm Eldest Princess of Great Yan.

398
00:17:37,330 --> 00:17:38,290
How dare you touch me!

399
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:39,220
Take her away!

400
00:17:40,290 --> 00:17:41,010
Zhao Ye,

401
00:17:41,290 --> 00:17:42,220
how dare you confine me?

402
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:44,220
This is the end
of today's court session.

403
00:17:45,290 --> 00:17:46,730
Eldest Princess, if you don't comply,

404
00:17:47,290 --> 00:17:48,460
you're disobeying my decree!

405
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:54,490
Your Highness.

406
00:17:54,490 --> 00:17:55,380
Xue Fangfei!

407
00:17:55,380 --> 00:17:56,770
Don't do that.

408
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:22,010
Xiao Heng,

409
00:18:22,460 --> 00:18:23,180
how dare you!

410
00:18:24,250 --> 00:18:25,380
From today onward,

411
00:18:26,090 --> 00:18:27,140
Without my order,

412
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:29,860
Eldest Princess is not allowed
to leave her residence!

413
00:18:32,940 --> 00:18:34,900
Today's court session has ended.

414
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:36,050
- Let go.
- Dismiss.

415
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:37,220
Xue Fangfei, just you wait!

416
00:19:17,900 --> 00:19:18,570
Father,

417
00:19:19,770 --> 00:19:20,900
I have a favour to ask.

418
00:19:21,660 --> 00:19:22,330
Go ahead.

419
00:19:22,980 --> 00:19:25,220
The former subordinates
of Magistrate Xue

420
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:26,570
and the people of Huaixiang
who came to the capital with me

421
00:19:27,010 --> 00:19:28,250
are in Ye Shijie's residence.

422
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,330
Since I brought them here,

423
00:19:30,660 --> 00:19:31,730
I should finish what I started.

424
00:19:32,290 --> 00:19:33,860
I want to treat them well
before I send them away.

425
00:19:34,860 --> 00:19:36,620
I have to go to Ye's Residence now.

426
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,570
After such a mess,

427
00:19:39,250 --> 00:19:41,250
you'll have to clean it up.

428
00:19:42,220 --> 00:19:43,980
Come back when you're done.

429
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:48,810
I think it's time we have a little talk.

430
00:19:50,530 --> 00:19:51,140
Yes,

431
00:19:51,770 --> 00:19:52,490
Father.

432
00:19:55,730 --> 00:19:56,570
Remember,

433
00:20:00,530 --> 00:20:02,380
you're a daughter from the Jiang family.

434
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:13,330
Little Leopard Cat?

435
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:16,250
You're quite interesting.

436
00:20:17,330 --> 00:20:19,180
Everyone in the capital is praising you

437
00:20:19,810 --> 00:20:21,090
for solving the wrongs

438
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:22,490
and redressing the injustice.

439
00:20:23,570 --> 00:20:25,220
What are you doing here

440
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:27,140
if you're not out there being praised?

441
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:29,250
What's the matter?

442
00:20:29,940 --> 00:20:31,250
I want to ask you a favour.

443
00:20:31,810 --> 00:20:32,490
What's it?

444
00:20:34,810 --> 00:20:36,570
There's a grave on Qingcheng Mountain

445
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:40,530
and I want you

446
00:20:42,460 --> 00:20:44,570
to dig up the bones

447
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:46,530
and rebury them for me.

448
00:20:53,940 --> 00:20:55,290
Who's buried in there?

449
00:20:57,860 --> 00:20:59,420
Why don't you go yourself?

450
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:01,620
Duke Su,

451
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,860
are you interrogating me?

452
00:21:05,180 --> 00:21:06,380
You could say that.

453
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:07,940
Fine.

454
00:21:08,570 --> 00:21:09,530
Consider I didn't say anything.

455
00:21:09,530 --> 00:21:10,180
Wait.

456
00:21:14,010 --> 00:21:15,330
I can dig the grave for you,

457
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:17,860
but it's a long way
to Qingcheng Mountain.

458
00:21:18,250 --> 00:21:18,860
It's boring.

459
00:21:19,940 --> 00:21:21,330
I don't want to go alone.

460
00:21:23,860 --> 00:21:24,770
What do you mean?

461
00:21:26,570 --> 00:21:27,180
Come with me.

462
00:21:47,290 --> 00:21:48,700
Why did you bring me here?

463
00:21:50,660 --> 00:21:53,860
I guess you want
to come here to say goodbye.

464
00:21:54,940 --> 00:21:56,570
I just want to forget about this place.

465
00:21:58,010 --> 00:21:59,380
If you want to forget this place,

466
00:22:00,490 --> 00:22:01,860
then why do you want to move it?

467
00:22:05,860 --> 00:22:06,860
You know why, and you're asking me.

468
00:22:07,330 --> 00:22:10,730
Isn't Xue Fangfei buried here?

469
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:19,460
Xue Fangfei is an unclean woman

470
00:22:19,460 --> 00:22:20,860
in the eyes of the world.

471
00:22:23,180 --> 00:22:24,810
She already lived a miserable life.

472
00:22:27,420 --> 00:22:29,940
Now that Eldest Princess
is thinking of digging the grave,

473
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,660
I must move her bones.

474
00:22:33,460 --> 00:22:35,090
I don't want anyone to disturb her.

475
00:22:36,250 --> 00:22:37,050
What about you?

476
00:22:39,090 --> 00:22:40,490
I don't want to disturb her, too.

477
00:22:43,980 --> 00:22:46,380
She was clean.

478
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:51,330
She was a good person.

479
00:22:52,900 --> 00:22:55,570
She thought she was in love
with a good man.

480
00:22:58,010 --> 00:23:00,940
She just wanted
to live a good life with him.

481
00:23:01,860 --> 00:23:02,660
And for that,

482
00:23:03,620 --> 00:23:05,730
she gave everything away,

483
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:09,730
including herself,

484
00:23:11,220 --> 00:23:12,050
and her family.

485
00:23:13,980 --> 00:23:15,250
But in the end,

486
00:23:16,460 --> 00:23:19,660
she's lying alone in this cold place.

487
00:23:21,380 --> 00:23:22,050
What else?

488
00:23:23,090 --> 00:23:25,770
She was a woman of noble status.

489
00:23:27,380 --> 00:23:29,380
She was a good woman.

490
00:23:29,940 --> 00:23:31,810
She didn't kill her mother
or her brother.

491
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,380
She just wanted to go home.

492
00:23:34,570 --> 00:23:35,380
And for that,

493
00:23:36,250 --> 00:23:38,980
she waited for ten years
at Qingcheng Mountain.

494
00:23:38,980 --> 00:23:40,010
Ten years.

495
00:23:42,010 --> 00:23:43,220
But in the end,

496
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:46,330
she's lying in this place too.

497
00:23:48,940 --> 00:23:50,700
I failed to protect her.

498
00:23:54,620 --> 00:23:55,900
You've done a great job.

499
00:23:56,900 --> 00:23:57,810
She won't blame you.

500
00:23:58,380 --> 00:23:59,460
You vindicated the Xue family,

501
00:24:00,620 --> 00:24:02,940
forced Jiang Yuanbai
to recognise his daughter

502
00:24:03,770 --> 00:24:05,660
and redressed the injustice
of the people of Huaixiang.

503
00:24:08,380 --> 00:24:09,490
As a pawn,

504
00:24:10,290 --> 00:24:11,530
I'm very impressed with you.

505
00:24:16,730 --> 00:24:18,140
Is there anything else
you want to tell her?

506
00:24:22,380 --> 00:24:23,380
I've said it all.

507
00:24:26,010 --> 00:24:27,250
Then I'll have someone

508
00:24:27,860 --> 00:24:28,770
replace her body.

509
00:24:35,290 --> 00:24:36,090
Duke Su,

510
00:24:37,090 --> 00:24:37,860
thank you

511
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:39,620
for helping me protect Li.

512
00:24:41,770 --> 00:24:42,620
So, Li,

513
00:24:44,010 --> 00:24:45,010
from today onward,

514
00:24:46,530 --> 00:24:48,420
you don't have to fear anyone anymore.

515
00:24:49,260 --> 00:24:56,620
♪Who wish for flower petals
to return to its core?♪

516
00:24:57,220 --> 00:25:04,660
♪Rekindle hot tears
flowing into the heart♪

517
00:25:12,730 --> 00:25:13,380
Take it.

518
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:14,530
Thank you.

519
00:25:17,620 --> 00:25:18,180
Boss,

520
00:25:18,900 --> 00:25:19,490
give me two.

521
00:25:19,490 --> 00:25:19,900
Okay.

522
00:25:23,420 --> 00:25:26,940
♪As I undress with no regrets♪

523
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:31,100
♪No water compares to the vast ocean♪

524
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:34,820
♪The right and wrongs
of a fleeting life♪

525
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:39,620
♪Not worth the pursuit♪

526
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:43,380
♪A formidable heart of iron and stone♪

527
00:25:44,140 --> 00:25:47,460
♪Yet, it bows in sadness
for love and sorrow♪

528
00:25:47,780 --> 00:25:51,420
♪Forgetting
the preciousness of the soul♪

529
00:25:52,860 --> 00:25:53,420
This one.

530
00:25:53,980 --> 00:25:55,620
Do you like this or this?

531
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:57,570
I think this is better.

532
00:25:58,140 --> 00:25:58,770
This?

533
00:26:07,810 --> 00:26:08,700
Second Lady Jiang.

534
00:26:24,730 --> 00:26:25,570
Mr. Shen.

535
00:26:27,460 --> 00:26:29,330
Second Lady Jiang, you look

536
00:26:30,490 --> 00:26:31,330
good today.

537
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:33,380
It's because I've figured something out.

538
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:35,460
I'd like to hear about it.

539
00:26:36,330 --> 00:26:37,810
Your late wife

540
00:26:39,860 --> 00:26:42,620
saved my life once from death.

541
00:26:43,490 --> 00:26:44,700
I used to wonder

542
00:26:46,220 --> 00:26:47,700
why a person
who couldn't protect herself

543
00:26:48,620 --> 00:26:50,700
would drag me back from hell.

544
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:53,810
I used to think
it was because of hatred,

545
00:26:54,530 --> 00:26:55,660
hatred of the world,

546
00:26:57,900 --> 00:26:59,180
hatred of her husband,

547
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:00,570
and that she was resentful.

548
00:27:02,330 --> 00:27:03,420
Now I understand.

549
00:27:04,050 --> 00:27:04,980
The world is vast,

550
00:27:05,980 --> 00:27:06,860
the country is prosperous,

551
00:27:07,530 --> 00:27:08,330
and the people are numerous.

552
00:27:10,490 --> 00:27:11,490
She saved me

553
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:14,010
because she's a wonderful person.

554
00:27:16,010 --> 00:27:17,490
She hasn't seen enough of this world.

555
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:21,770
How can a mean, pathetic man

556
00:27:22,380 --> 00:27:24,010
be her obsession?

557
00:27:30,810 --> 00:27:32,050
Is that really what she thinks?

558
00:27:33,530 --> 00:27:34,530
You will know.

559
00:27:35,100 --> 00:27:40,020
♪If there are no happy memories♪

560
00:27:42,540 --> 00:27:47,820
♪How can we traverse
the forbidden land of sorrow?♪

561
00:27:49,820 --> 00:27:55,500
♪Two cold and unfeeling bodies♪

562
00:27:56,180 --> 00:28:03,460
♪Holding hands,
can we get through the snow season?♪

563
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:12,300
♪The depth of the sea, unfathomable♪

564
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:18,380
[Ma's Restaurant]
♪Can it bury yesterday's sighs?♪

565
00:28:18,380 --> 00:28:19,620
[Xiang's Restaurant]

566
00:28:19,620 --> 00:28:26,740
♪Continue to live,
exhausting all courage♪

567
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:34,220
♪Continue to love,
until the breath runs out♪

568
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:41,940
♪Traversing half a lifetime of
loneliness, just to meet you♪

569
00:28:42,860 --> 00:28:49,060
♪After the hardships,
never to part again♪

570
00:28:56,140 --> 00:28:57,900
This was a mistake on my part.

571
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:01,890
I'm willing to accept the punishment.

572
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:04,660
Don't blame yourself,
Grand Chancellor Li.

573
00:29:06,010 --> 00:29:07,860
You've done a great job.

574
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:09,860
It's because of my faulty planning.

575
00:29:10,140 --> 00:29:11,980
You've suffered.

576
00:29:12,330 --> 00:29:13,330
Your Highness...

577
00:29:13,980 --> 00:29:16,010
I'm going to have to rely on you

578
00:29:16,570 --> 00:29:18,290
while I'm grounded.

579
00:29:19,380 --> 00:29:20,810
I, Li Zhongnan,

580
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:25,050
will be at the beck and call
of Your Highness and King Cheng.

581
00:29:29,050 --> 00:29:29,860
Grand Chancellor Li,

582
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:31,220
get up.

583
00:29:32,730 --> 00:29:33,940
Thank you, Your Highness.

584
00:29:39,250 --> 00:29:40,810
I have a secret letter here.

585
00:29:41,700 --> 00:29:43,250
Please give it to Imperial Diviner.

586
00:29:46,490 --> 00:29:47,900
Tell Mr. Shen to come in.

587
00:29:56,980 --> 00:29:57,860
Mr. Shen,

588
00:29:58,700 --> 00:29:59,980
you've been kneeling all night.

589
00:30:00,490 --> 00:30:01,730
Now it's your turn.

590
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:16,810
Shen Yurong,

591
00:30:16,980 --> 00:30:18,420
do you take me for a fool?

592
00:30:19,770 --> 00:30:21,180
Your Highness is a noble lady.

593
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:23,900
If Xue Fangfei's affair
is exposed in Imperial Court today,

594
00:30:24,940 --> 00:30:25,810
I don't care if I die,

595
00:30:26,290 --> 00:30:28,810
but if my mother, younger sister
and Your Highness get dragged into this,

596
00:30:29,330 --> 00:30:30,700
and your reputation is damaged,

597
00:30:31,290 --> 00:30:32,050
I will be sinful.

598
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:33,290
So

599
00:30:35,010 --> 00:30:36,090
she can only be Jiang Li.

600
00:30:36,090 --> 00:30:36,570
[Virtue and Growth]

601
00:30:36,570 --> 00:30:37,530
I don't care who she is.

602
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,770
She must die now.

603
00:30:40,530 --> 00:30:41,810
It's easy to kill her.

604
00:30:42,900 --> 00:30:44,490
Your Highness don't have
to get your hands dirty.

605
00:30:44,730 --> 00:30:46,090
Just like today's incident,

606
00:30:47,250 --> 00:30:48,980
I warned Your Highness not to intervene,

607
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:51,010
but Your Highness didn't believe me

608
00:30:51,770 --> 00:30:52,730
and acted rashly

609
00:30:53,660 --> 00:30:55,180
to your own detriment.

610
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:57,620
Then what should I do?

611
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,250
Jiang Li has many enemies.

612
00:31:01,090 --> 00:31:02,090
Your Highness can

613
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:04,860
use someone to kill her.

614
00:31:07,140 --> 00:31:08,490
Can you bring yourself to kill her?

615
00:31:09,730 --> 00:31:10,490
For you,

616
00:31:12,810 --> 00:31:13,900
I can kill anyone.

617
00:31:17,490 --> 00:31:19,900
It's heartbreaking the way you talk.

618
00:31:20,490 --> 00:31:23,090
It's a pity I can't
adore you these days.

619
00:31:52,180 --> 00:31:52,660
My Lord,

620
00:31:52,900 --> 00:31:54,500
His Majesty said we
should investigate to the end.

621
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:55,850
How can we let Li Zhongnan go?

622
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:58,020
Leave an escape gap
for the surrounded enemy

623
00:31:58,570 --> 00:31:59,810
and don't push
the desperate enemy too hard.

624
00:32:00,420 --> 00:32:01,130
What does it mean?

625
00:32:06,660 --> 00:32:07,290
Lu Ji,

626
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:08,980
explain it.

627
00:32:09,570 --> 00:32:11,260
Even Wanning,
who's never been punished before,

628
00:32:11,260 --> 00:32:12,220
was punished by His Majesty.

629
00:32:12,850 --> 00:32:14,460
If we pick on Li Zhongnan at this time,

630
00:32:14,810 --> 00:32:15,810
it may cause trouble.

631
00:32:17,290 --> 00:32:18,500
When the sword is sheathed,

632
00:32:19,050 --> 00:32:20,660
it will kill.

633
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:37,770
After eliminating Li Zhongnan's men,

634
00:32:37,770 --> 00:32:39,180
Wei Qian, Zhang Kun and the others,

635
00:32:39,850 --> 00:32:42,260
Li Zhongnan won't be able
to make a move again for a while.

636
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:45,260
That's the end of the Huaixiang case.

637
00:32:45,900 --> 00:32:46,660
I guess

638
00:32:47,530 --> 00:32:49,290
Wanning still has cards in her hand.

639
00:32:50,130 --> 00:32:51,370
What should we do next?

640
00:32:51,940 --> 00:32:52,660
Wen Ji,

641
00:32:53,050 --> 00:32:53,660
tell me.

642
00:32:54,130 --> 00:32:55,420
Well... I...

643
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:57,220
Don't stammer.

644
00:32:57,460 --> 00:32:58,610
Think it over before talking

645
00:32:58,660 --> 00:32:59,700
so that you won't get punished.

646
00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:01,130
My Lord,

647
00:33:01,330 --> 00:33:02,420
give me a moment to think.

648
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:03,980
You have to think about this?

649
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:05,700
You shall receive your punishment.

650
00:33:09,260 --> 00:33:10,460
Just watch what's going to happen.

651
00:33:10,980 --> 00:33:11,940
Idiot.

652
00:33:14,530 --> 00:33:15,370
Something's wrong.

653
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:17,020
The Lord is asking what to do.

654
00:33:17,090 --> 00:33:19,020
Watch what's going to happen
means do nothing.

655
00:33:19,260 --> 00:33:19,900
This isn't fair,

656
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:20,330
My Lord.

657
00:33:20,330 --> 00:33:21,460
Why did you just ask a random question?

658
00:33:22,610 --> 00:33:34,180
[The North]
Stop the boat and ask for help.

659
00:33:35,290 --> 00:33:46,770
[King Cheng]
By the accent, you're my countryman.

660
00:33:47,850 --> 00:33:57,660
My home is near Jiujiang.

661
00:34:00,050 --> 00:34:01,090
Your Highness, please spare me.

662
00:34:01,290 --> 00:34:02,700
What nonsense did you sing?

663
00:34:04,020 --> 00:34:05,530
Isn't there anyone who can sing?

664
00:34:08,130 --> 00:34:09,050
Your Highness, please spare me.

665
00:34:09,340 --> 00:34:10,530
Your Highness, please spare me.

666
00:34:10,530 --> 00:34:12,820
We can't find someone like Taohong
in the north border.

667
00:34:13,380 --> 00:34:15,610
Unless we can find in the Zhongyuan.

668
00:34:17,460 --> 00:34:18,170
Guys,

669
00:34:19,730 --> 00:34:22,050
you've been fighting with me
for so many years,

670
00:34:22,610 --> 00:34:24,610
if you can't even watch a good opera,

671
00:34:24,940 --> 00:34:25,690
you can tolerate it,

672
00:34:25,690 --> 00:34:26,420
but I can't.

673
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:29,780
The time for achieving glory is coming.

674
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:32,530
When we take over the Zhongyuan,

675
00:34:32,940 --> 00:34:35,340
we'll enjoy whatever opera

676
00:34:35,340 --> 00:34:36,250
we want,

677
00:34:36,460 --> 00:34:39,650
and get any woman we want.

678
00:34:39,940 --> 00:34:50,210
King Cheng! King Cheng! King Cheng!

679
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:05,940
Your Highness,

680
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:08,420
Eldest Princess has been confined.

681
00:35:09,130 --> 00:35:10,380
That crazy sister of mine,

682
00:35:11,130 --> 00:35:12,570
I thought she had some ability,

683
00:35:13,300 --> 00:35:15,130
but she's such a disappointment.

684
00:35:15,860 --> 00:35:17,130
The cold season is here in the north.

685
00:35:18,050 --> 00:35:19,210
Now the gold mines are closed

686
00:35:20,050 --> 00:35:21,170
and the Ministry of War is giving us

687
00:35:21,170 --> 00:35:22,300
lesser wages and rations every year.

688
00:35:22,690 --> 00:35:23,420
At this rate,

689
00:35:24,530 --> 00:35:25,460
we'll have a hard time.

690
00:35:25,940 --> 00:35:26,860
As long as we achieve victory,

691
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:29,530
my brother in the palace
will definitely give us wages and rations.

692
00:35:30,250 --> 00:35:31,210
But Dai Country

693
00:35:32,090 --> 00:35:32,900
hasn't made a move lately.

694
00:35:33,300 --> 00:35:35,420
If there's nothing, make something.

695
00:35:36,690 --> 00:35:38,730
As long as we make it look like
Dai Country is invading,

696
00:35:39,530 --> 00:35:42,650
we'll fight the invaders
with all our strength

697
00:35:44,090 --> 00:35:45,340
in the north.

698
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:49,610
I'll go to the border to create a riot.

699
00:35:50,420 --> 00:35:51,980
I wish Your Highness
a successful victory

700
00:35:52,340 --> 00:35:53,570
over the invaders in advance.

701
00:35:57,820 --> 00:36:00,690
[Conceal the talent and draw no attention]
Rong, why do you keep yourself locked up?

702
00:36:01,050 --> 00:36:02,860
What did Eldest Princess tell you?

703
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:04,170
Tell us.

704
00:36:04,170 --> 00:36:05,130
Yes, Yurong.

705
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:06,570
You're scaring us.

706
00:36:06,780 --> 00:36:08,820
You're not to blame for what happened
to Her Highness, are you?

707
00:36:09,250 --> 00:36:10,420
You shouldn't have

708
00:36:10,530 --> 00:36:12,570
disobeyed Her Highness at the court.

709
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:15,090
If you don't care about Her Highness,

710
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:17,420
you must care about us.

711
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:20,610
I'm just an old widow,

712
00:36:20,780 --> 00:36:23,530
but I pity your sister,
who's still unmarried.

713
00:36:24,130 --> 00:36:26,020
I'm counting on Her Highness

714
00:36:26,130 --> 00:36:28,980
to find a good match for your sister.

715
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:29,570
Get lost!

716
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:34,730
Forget it, Mother.

717
00:36:35,780 --> 00:36:37,460
Yurong must be tired today.

718
00:36:38,210 --> 00:36:39,610
Let's not bother him.

719
00:36:40,050 --> 00:36:41,250
He knows what to do.

720
00:37:13,020 --> 00:37:14,300
I used to wonder

721
00:37:14,690 --> 00:37:16,250
why a person who
couldn't protect herself

722
00:37:16,460 --> 00:37:18,610
would drag me back from hell.

723
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:20,940
I used to think
it was because of hatred,

724
00:37:21,530 --> 00:37:22,690
hatred of the world,

725
00:37:23,380 --> 00:37:24,650
hatred of her husband,

726
00:37:25,170 --> 00:37:28,050
How can a mean, pathetic man

727
00:37:28,300 --> 00:37:29,900
be her obsession?

728
00:37:42,170 --> 00:37:45,090
Now the turmoil
in the Jiang family is finally over.

729
00:37:45,610 --> 00:37:48,020
You can finally rest assured, can't you?

730
00:37:49,050 --> 00:37:51,690
Who do you think Li looks like?

731
00:37:52,250 --> 00:37:53,860
Master Jiang, of course.

732
00:37:56,090 --> 00:37:57,530
As a woman,

733
00:37:58,420 --> 00:38:01,900
she has the courage
to fight for justice.

734
00:38:02,020 --> 00:38:02,940
In my opinion,

735
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:05,050
she's like Old Master Jiang.

736
00:38:05,130 --> 00:38:07,820
The blood of the Jiang family
runs in Second Lady's veins,

737
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:11,650
of course she has inherited
her ancestor's character.

738
00:38:11,980 --> 00:38:14,340
We've misjudged her for so many years,

739
00:38:15,460 --> 00:38:16,780
we owe her so much.

740
00:38:16,780 --> 00:38:19,860
Second Lady's so sensible.
She won't mind.

741
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:21,300
You can't say that.

742
00:38:21,730 --> 00:38:22,940
She's big-hearted,

743
00:38:23,130 --> 00:38:24,730
but she's still young.

744
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:26,530
She was away all these years

745
00:38:26,690 --> 00:38:28,250
and she didn't miss
the warmth of the family?

746
00:38:28,780 --> 00:38:32,210
When she comes back,
I'm going to give her a treat.

747
00:38:33,050 --> 00:38:34,090
Tell those in the kitchen

748
00:38:34,780 --> 00:38:37,500
to prepare a feast for Second Lady
to welcome her return.

749
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:38,380
Yes.

750
00:38:40,570 --> 00:38:41,170
Madam Ji,

751
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:42,690
I've heard that Old Madam

752
00:38:42,690 --> 00:38:44,090
has no intention of blaming Jiang Li

753
00:38:44,730 --> 00:38:46,340
and is preparing a feast
to welcome her return.

754
00:38:46,690 --> 00:38:48,610
Now that Jiang Li is gaining fame,

755
00:38:49,130 --> 00:38:51,050
she's bringing honor
to the Jiang family.

756
00:38:51,570 --> 00:38:53,250
Of course Old Madam
would like to flatter her.

757
00:38:53,500 --> 00:38:55,340
It's hard to wait for something
to happen to Jiang Li

758
00:38:55,690 --> 00:38:57,130
and she was in Court
of Judicial Review's prison.

759
00:38:57,210 --> 00:38:59,250
Why did you help to get her out?

760
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:03,650
When the nest has tumbled,
all its eggs will be destroyed.

761
00:39:04,130 --> 00:39:05,020
She's smart.

762
00:39:06,090 --> 00:39:07,690
She knows that she's tied

763
00:39:07,980 --> 00:39:10,380
to the Jiang family at the moment.

764
00:39:12,250 --> 00:39:15,170
Even I had to save her.

765
00:39:15,170 --> 00:39:17,650
Then we won't be able
to deal with her anymore.

766
00:39:17,860 --> 00:39:19,130
Jindai, sit down.

767
00:39:23,130 --> 00:39:24,860
I was willing to help her,

768
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:26,650
and now Master Jiang and Old Madam

769
00:39:26,650 --> 00:39:29,050
are willing to host a feast
for her, too, aren't they?

770
00:39:29,050 --> 00:39:29,860
Does Jiang Li appreciate

771
00:39:29,860 --> 00:39:32,130
the Jiang family's kindness
in her heart?

772
00:39:32,460 --> 00:39:35,300
Let them flatter her all they want.

773
00:39:35,460 --> 00:39:38,570
They won't know the pain
until they're trampled on.

774
00:39:38,980 --> 00:39:40,020
As for us,

775
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:42,170
we just need to remind

776
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:43,820
Old Madam at the right time

777
00:39:44,020 --> 00:39:47,340
to let her know who Jiang Li
regards as her family.

778
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:48,340
That's it.

779
00:39:48,340 --> 00:39:49,940
You're really wise.

780
00:39:50,170 --> 00:39:53,820
I've heard that Magistrate Xue

781
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:56,860
and the people of Huaixiang
are all settled in the Ye family.

782
00:39:57,210 --> 00:39:58,420
Yes.

783
00:39:58,940 --> 00:40:01,730
I've heard that the Ye family is so rich

784
00:40:02,130 --> 00:40:03,650
that they're planning
a celebration banquet

785
00:40:04,050 --> 00:40:07,170
for Jiang Li
and the people of Huaixiang.

786
00:40:07,170 --> 00:40:07,780
Very good.

787
00:40:08,530 --> 00:40:10,050
Try to find out the date.

788
00:40:10,650 --> 00:40:12,780
The feast arranged by Old Madam

789
00:40:13,730 --> 00:40:16,300
shall be held on the same day
as their celebration banquet.

790
00:40:16,860 --> 00:40:20,250
Let's see if Jiang Li is willing
to leave the people of Huaixiang behind

791
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:23,690
or if she wants to leave Master Jiang
and Old Madam out in the cold.

792
00:40:23,820 --> 00:40:24,570
I got it.

793
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:29,940
[Ye's Residence]

794
00:40:44,770 --> 00:40:45,770
Thank you, sir.

795
00:40:46,420 --> 00:40:48,060
How is Magistrate Xue's condition?

796
00:40:48,650 --> 00:40:50,820
Magistrate Xue's flesh wounds

797
00:40:51,210 --> 00:40:53,090
will heal in time,

798
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:56,340
but his delusional disorder
is not going to go away.

799
00:40:56,460 --> 00:40:57,980
What is delusional disorder?

800
00:40:58,170 --> 00:41:00,210
This disorder
makes someone feel restless,

801
00:41:00,290 --> 00:41:02,250
feeling that his soul has left his body,

802
00:41:02,570 --> 00:41:03,690
having nightmares,

803
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:05,730
forgetting family,

804
00:41:06,130 --> 00:41:07,730
forgetting past events

805
00:41:07,900 --> 00:41:09,610
and forgetting oneself.

806
00:41:09,860 --> 00:41:13,420
In my opinion, it's because
Magistrate Xue lost his children

807
00:41:13,580 --> 00:41:14,950
and was tortured

808
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:17,030
in a wrongful case,

809
00:41:17,030 --> 00:41:18,950
so his heart aches
and his mind gets lost.

810
00:41:18,950 --> 00:41:21,620
It's an illness
that builds up over time.

811
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:22,660
How can it be cured?

812
00:41:23,030 --> 00:41:26,350
The pain in heart is like
a thousand feet of ice,

813
00:41:26,580 --> 00:41:28,140
it can't be melted in a day.

814
00:42:02,540 --> 00:42:03,790
It's said that the experts
are in the people.

815
00:42:04,900 --> 00:42:06,290
If the imperial physician
can't cure him,

816
00:42:06,420 --> 00:42:08,060
it doesn't mean
that the folk physicians can't either.

817
00:42:08,540 --> 00:42:09,900
No matter how much money
I have to spend,

818
00:42:10,250 --> 00:42:12,060
I'll cure Magistrate Xue.

819
00:42:12,420 --> 00:42:15,020
This is a favour I owe the Xue family.

820
00:42:16,170 --> 00:42:17,210
You shouldn't repay it for me.

821
00:42:17,770 --> 00:42:20,250
You've helped me so much along the way.

822
