850
00:43:39,650 --> 00:43:41,170
Guys, come on. Try this.

851
00:43:41,170 --> 00:43:44,420
A toast to Magistrate Xue's
redress of injustice.

852
00:43:44,900 --> 00:43:47,540
Come on, let's drink.

853
00:43:47,900 --> 00:43:49,260
One, two, three, bottoms up!

854
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:50,660
Come on, bottoms up!

855
00:43:51,180 --> 00:43:53,990
What are your plans for the future?

856
00:43:54,660 --> 00:43:56,470
I'm going back to Huaixiang for a while.

857
00:43:56,620 --> 00:43:58,350
If a new magistrate comes,

858
00:43:58,940 --> 00:44:00,820
I'll serve under him

859
00:44:01,020 --> 00:44:02,060
and continue to work for Huaixiang.

860
00:44:02,460 --> 00:44:04,700
That's right. We don't want
anything more than

861
00:44:05,020 --> 00:44:06,900
to live peacefully in our hometown

862
00:44:07,660 --> 00:44:08,540
and return to our old jobs.

863
00:44:08,900 --> 00:44:11,420
Second Lady Jiang, like your Uncle Liu,

864
00:44:12,180 --> 00:44:14,470
I just want to live a good life.

865
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:18,260
I'm going back, too, Li.

866
00:44:18,380 --> 00:44:19,460
Why are you leaving, too?

867
00:44:19,540 --> 00:44:21,950
Your mother's greatest regret in life

868
00:44:23,060 --> 00:44:24,140
was that as a woman,

869
00:44:25,100 --> 00:44:26,790
she couldn't wander the world

870
00:44:26,790 --> 00:44:27,990
like a man.

871
00:44:28,140 --> 00:44:29,470
I'm relieved

872
00:44:29,540 --> 00:44:30,510
that you're doing well.

873
00:44:30,820 --> 00:44:32,170
Shijie will take care of you
in the capital,

874
00:44:32,420 --> 00:44:35,540
so I'll go and explore
and take a nice look at the world

875
00:44:35,860 --> 00:44:37,020
for your mother.

876
00:44:37,620 --> 00:44:38,390
But don't worry.

877
00:44:38,740 --> 00:44:41,660
I'm always your Third Uncle

878
00:44:42,100 --> 00:44:43,430
and Ye's Residence is always your home.

879
00:44:43,830 --> 00:44:46,310
And I'll always be there for you.

880
00:44:47,390 --> 00:44:49,140
Second Lady Jiang, and me.

881
00:44:49,540 --> 00:44:51,310
Second Lady Jiang,
don't forget about me.

882
00:44:51,430 --> 00:44:52,950
Lady Jiang, if you ask us,

883
00:44:53,180 --> 00:44:54,580
we'll do whatever you want.

884
00:44:54,910 --> 00:44:56,220
Yes, you have us.

885
00:44:56,220 --> 00:44:57,430
Yes, and me.

886
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:04,700
I'm deeply grateful

887
00:45:06,100 --> 00:45:07,470
for your kindness.

888
00:45:07,950 --> 00:45:09,060
I'd like to thank you

889
00:45:10,140 --> 00:45:13,910
for risking your lives to overturn
Magistrate Xue's conviction.

890
00:45:14,510 --> 00:45:17,430
People unfated will part ways, but those
fated to meet will eventually meet.

891
00:45:17,990 --> 00:45:19,990
I'd like to propose
a farewell toast to you all.

892
00:45:20,310 --> 00:45:22,140
May we meet again in the future.

893
00:45:22,430 --> 00:45:25,140
Sure. May we meet again.

894
00:45:25,140 --> 00:45:26,140
See you again.

895
00:45:26,350 --> 00:45:27,030
See you again.

896
00:45:31,990 --> 00:45:32,390
Come on.

897
00:45:32,700 --> 00:45:33,910
Quick, sit down.

898
00:45:34,060 --> 00:45:36,220
Come on, fill my bowl up. Come on.

899
