- Sit down.

900
00:45:40,260 --> 00:45:41,430
- Come on.
- Here's to you.

901
00:45:41,910 --> 00:45:42,740
- Come on.
- Let's drink.

902
00:45:42,740 --> 00:45:44,350
Second Lady Jiang, let's drink.

903
00:45:45,470 --> 00:45:46,350
Young Master, dig in.

904
00:45:46,700 --> 00:45:48,510
Someone from the Jiang family
is asking to see Second Lady Jiang.

905
00:45:49,540 --> 00:45:50,350
I'll go out and take a look.

906
00:45:56,510 --> 00:45:58,100
Come on. Let's drink. Come on.

907
00:45:58,100 --> 00:45:58,660
- Come on.
- Quick.

908
00:45:58,870 --> 00:45:59,700
- Here's to you.
- Okay.

909
00:45:59,700 --> 00:46:01,950
Second Lady, are you having dinner?

910
00:46:02,870 --> 00:46:04,260
Have you forgotten about the family?

911
00:46:04,350 --> 00:46:05,950
Madam Ji is hosting a feast
for you at home.

912
00:46:06,220 --> 00:46:07,830
She's waiting to welcome your return.

913
00:46:07,950 --> 00:46:09,540
When did anyone tell me that?

914
00:46:09,700 --> 00:46:11,140
I told Bai Xue this afternoon.

915
00:46:11,620 --> 00:46:13,140
Didn't Bai Xue inform you?

916
00:46:13,430 --> 00:46:15,260
You know I'm not at home all day today.

917
00:46:15,740 --> 00:46:17,220
Did you ask a girl to look for me

918
00:46:17,390 --> 00:46:18,870
all over town to deliver a message?

919
00:46:19,100 --> 00:46:20,830
I had no choice, didn't I?

920
00:46:21,180 --> 00:46:24,060
Who told you to stay out all day?

921
00:46:24,350 --> 00:46:25,430
There's a feast at home,

922
00:46:26,260 --> 00:46:28,180
but you didn't tell me earlier
so I could help out.

923
00:46:28,700 --> 00:46:30,030
It's already late

924
00:46:30,390 --> 00:46:32,060
and you're only looking for me now.

925
00:46:32,830 --> 00:46:34,740
Could it be
that Mother doesn't treat me as family

926
00:46:34,790 --> 00:46:35,870
or

927
00:46:35,950 --> 00:46:38,350
that she knew I was bidding farewell
to the people of Huaixiang

928
00:46:38,580 --> 00:46:39,910
and arranged for it
to have taken place on this day?

929
00:46:40,100 --> 00:46:42,740
Second Lady, Madam Ji will get upset

930
00:46:43,180 --> 00:46:44,790
if you misinterpret her good intentions.

931
00:46:45,100 --> 00:46:46,510
She's been working very hard

932
00:46:46,620 --> 00:46:47,950
to prepare the feast
to welcome your return.

933
00:46:49,100 --> 00:46:50,870
The banquet inside has already begun.

934
00:46:51,180 --> 00:46:53,260
Mother's slow to inform me.

935
00:46:53,470 --> 00:46:55,180
If I leave now,

936
00:46:55,390 --> 00:46:57,950
people will say the Jiangs
don't know manners

937
00:46:58,100 --> 00:46:59,350
and ruin my father's reputation.

938
00:46:59,620 --> 00:47:00,830
If that's the case,

939
00:47:01,390 --> 00:47:03,470
I'll go back and inform Madam Ji

940
00:47:03,580 --> 00:47:05,910
that we'll hold a feast
to welcome your return next time.

941
00:47:06,620 --> 00:47:07,620
Thank you, Madam Sun.

